###  https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rule-based_system#Production_system_rules
<https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rule-based_system#Production_system_rules> rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual .


###  https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Semantics_(programming_languages)#Approaches
<https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Semantics_(programming_languages)#Approaches> rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual .


